name: Wordle
content:
Description: 10,000 valid "Wordle" guesses and answers, sourced from the New York Times.

[Source](https://www.nytimes.com/games/wordle/main.bfba912f.js)

Columns:

* validWordleGuess (string): words that are valid guesses
* validWordleAnswer (string): words that can be used as answers
